sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 로그인 회원
    participant JSP as reserve.jsp
    participant C as HospitalController
    participant S as HospitalServiceImpl
    participant M as HospitalMapper
    participant DB as Oracle

    User->>JSP: 예약하기 클릭
    JSP->>C: GET /hospital/reserve
    C->>C: session memberInfo 확인
    C->>S: getHospitalById getPetListForReserve
    S->>M: SELECT TB_HOSPITAL TB_PET
    M->>DB: 조회
    C-->>JSP: hospital petList

    User->>JSP: 예약 정보 입력
    JSP->>C: POST /hospital/reserve
    C->>C: vo.memberNo targetId 설정
    C->>S: createHospitalReservation(vo)
    S->>S: PENDING resvNo 생성
    S->>M: insertReservation
    M->>DB: INSERT TB_RESERVATION
    C-->>JSP: redirect complete
